sequenceDiagram
    participant Init as Init Container<br/>(odh-pipelines-components)
    participant Vol as Shared Volume<br/>/config/managed-pipelines
    participant KFP as KFP API Server
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant S3 as AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC as PVC Workspace<br/>Filesystem
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Trainer as Kubeflow Trainer<br/>Worker Pods
    participant vLLM as vLLM Engine<br/>Local
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant LS as Llama Stack API<br/>HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Init,KFP: Flow 1: Managed Pipeline Staging (Platform Startup)
        Init->>Init: generate_managed_pipelines.py<br/>Compiles pipeline.py → YAML
        Init->>Vol: Copy compiled YAMLs<br/>Filesystem
        KFP->>Vol: Read managed pipelines<br/>Filesystem
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,MR: Flow 2: Fine-Tuning Pipeline (LoRA/OSFT/SFT)
        User->>KFP: Submit fine-tuning pipeline
        KFP->>S3: dataset_download<br/>HTTPS/443 | AWS IAM
        KFP->>HF: dataset_download<br/>HTTPS/443 | HF_TOKEN
        KFP->>PVC: Store dataset<br/>Filesystem
        KFP->>K8s: train_model: Create TrainingJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
        K8s->>Trainer: Schedule worker pods
        Trainer->>PVC: Write model checkpoints<br/>Filesystem
        Trainer-->>KFP: Stream training logs
        KFP->>vLLM: universal_llm_evaluator<br/>Load model, run benchmarks
        vLLM-->>KFP: Evaluation metrics
        KFP->>MR: Register model + metadata<br/>HTTP/8080 | No auth (insecure)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,LS: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoRAG pipeline
        KFP->>S3: test_data_loader: Load test JSON<br/>HTTPS/443 | AWS IAM
        KFP->>S3: documents_discovery: List objects<br/>HTTPS/443 | AWS IAM
        KFP->>S3: text_extraction: Download docs<br/>HTTPS/443 | AWS IAM
        KFP->>KFP: text_extraction: Docling extraction<br/>Local
        KFP->>LS: search_space_preparation<br/>HTTPS | Bearer token
        KFP->>LS: rag_templates_optimization<br/>Indexing + inference | API key
        KFP->>KFP: leaderboard_evaluation<br/>Local (pattern.json)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 245)
        Note over User,PVC: Flow 4: AutoML Tabular Training Pipeline
        User->>KFP: Submit AutoML pipeline
        KFP->>S3: automl_data_loader: Stream CSV<br/>HTTPS/443 | AWS IAM
        KFP->>PVC: Store train/test splits<br/>Filesystem
        KFP->>PVC: autogluon_models_training<br/>Local AutoGluon training
        KFP->>PVC: leaderboard_evaluation<br/>Local model metrics
    end
